Visual Suggestions 5

SUGGESTION:

1. Community-oriented policing, where more officers would build stronger relationships with community members should be encouraged to avoid unnecessary killing

2. Restrict officers from using deadly force unless all reasonable alternatives have been exhausted

3. Carry a less-lethal weapon and ban using force on a person for talking back or as punishment for running away
